Description:  Crystallographic refinement
DescDetail: <<
This updates the ccp4-installed refmac to version 5.2 (5.1999 - don't ask).
The REFMAC program can carry out rigid body, tls, restrained or unrestrained 
refinement against Xray data, or idealisation of a macromolecular structure. 
It minimises the coordinate parameters to satisfy either a Maximum 
Likelihood or Least Squares residual. 
.
This version assumes you have already installed the
CCP4 macromolecular crystallography program suite with fink.
This version compiles with Apple's Lapack/Blas
<< 
